<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-12-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-11-09T00:00:00-00:44" n="667" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d667">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>Turkey and the United States on August 16, 1951, in an exchange of
                                notes, amended the Economic Cooperation Agreement of July 4, 1948,
                                as previously amended. For the texts of these notes which entered
                                into force upon signature, see <gloss target="#t_TIAS1">TIAS</gloss>
                                No. 2392, printed in 3 <gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> (pt. 1)
                                54.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>